  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/f3b867ba4aaa2c0764e3608dba9c4dc2.poster.avif?t=1766413976\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/f3b867ba4aaa2c0764e3608dba9c4dc2.webm?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/f3b867ba4aaa2c0764e3608dba9c4dc2.mp4?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>PLAY</u></strong></i> through worlds as Belle with the help of her companion Chime. Defeat a variety of enemies and avoid obstacles while you leap through each level! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/2ddeaba2dcfdc4a31c4708e21be667f9.poster.avif?t=1766413976\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/2ddeaba2dcfdc4a31c4708e21be667f9.webm?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/2ddeaba2dcfdc4a31c4708e21be667f9.mp4?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>DISCOVER</u></strong></i> hidden secrets and collectibles hidden in every area. They might just come in handy later!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/d2effd0136f305d20203f814f7d96c2a.poster.avif?t=1766413976\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/d2effd0136f305d20203f814f7d96c2a.webm?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/d2effd0136f305d20203f814f7d96c2a.mp4?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>CHALLENGE</u></strong></i> tough bosses on your journey in order to advance to more areas. Each one has a unique set of skills that you have to adjust for! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/2cafb7a31c502d04604e414e39437e56.poster.avif?t=1766413976\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/2cafb7a31c502d04604e414e39437e56.webm?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/2cafb7a31c502d04604e414e39437e56.mp4?t=1766413976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>CONNECT</u></i></strong> with all kinds of colorful characters at every location. They might have tasks to perform, items to sell, or just a nice chat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726760/extras/cedb9508541340f2aea3fb0f0f2dbea8.avif?t=1766413976\" width=780 height=240 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable character color palettes and main menu backgrounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 10 unique areas, totally more than 50 stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous magical baked goods and ancient artifacts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless secrets hidden throughout</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A killer retro themed soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several side quest story lines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over a dozen bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty more!</p></li></ul>",
